<hymn_number>5235</hymn_number>
<title>yạ mkẖlṣy ạṣḥbny</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yā mukẖalĩṣī ạṣ̊ḥabanĩy .. kun̊ lī daẘmaⁿạ mur̊sẖidaⁿạ
 bīamīnika ạḥ̊rusanĩy .. kaẙ lạ ạảkẖ̊sẖay̱ ạảḥadaⁿạ

[V2]
 ạlqrạr: (las̊tu min̊ sẖariⁿ̃ ạảkẖāfu .. fāh̊dinī ḥaẙtẖu turīd̊)2
 (bilạ ḍajariⁿ ạảsīru .. bal̊ biại̹ymāniⁿ waṭīd̊)2

[V3]
 2- ạiṣ̊gẖa lī ʿin̊da nidāyỉy .. ạ̉smiʿanĩy ṣawtaka
 ṣawtuka ạl̊ḥulwu ʿzạyỉy .. ạ̉nta kẖilĩy waḥdaka

[V4]
 3- laysa man yuʿzĩy qlby .. ḥīna tahjumu ạl̊kẖuṭūb
 ạ̹lạã ạ̉nta yạ ḥabyby .. tartẖī lī waqta ạlkurūb

[V5]
 4- sir maʿy ạ̉yạ ḥabyby .. qawĩ ạ̹ymạny ạlḍãʿyf
 sā̉rạka ʿan qarybi .. bijmạlika ạllãṭīf</lyrics>
</song>